data.title: Minnesota Vacations & Travel Guide: Explore Minnesota
data.meta_description: Your complete inspiration and travel planning guide to the state of Minnesota, with trip ideas, lodging, attractions, events, free brochures and more. Find Minnesota resorts, campgrounds, and events, plus Minnesota activities like hiking, biking, shopping, theater, and arts on ExploreMinnesota.com
data.text:
Whether you’re planning a visit or pondering a move, Minnesota — a state of seemingly endless possibilities — is ready to welcome you.

Need a little more encouragement? Here are some trip-planning tools and our latest inspo-oriented travel guides, listicles, and itineraries.
